verbose_text: Our FCM data revealed that Notch enhanced the proliferation of MSCs by decreasing the percentage of cells in the G0/G1 phase, and increasing the percentage of cells in the S phase In conclusion, we demonstrated that Notch signaling can potentiate the BMP9 induced osteogenic differentiation of MSCs.
evidence: Notch signaling can potentiate the BMP9-induced osteogenic differentiation
